node.title: Celtics' Hayward could miss four weeks with ankle sprain - NBC Sports Boston
node.description: The Celtics could be without Gordon Hayward for the next month after he sprained his ankle Monday night.

node.title: Practice Report 8/18: Watch Out, Lamar Jackson's Deep Passing Looks Better - BaltimoreRavens.com
node.description: Miles Boykin had the most catches in practice, including on highlight-reel snag. Rookie wideout Devin Duvernay hauls in two deep passes, showing off his speed. Tavon Young looks back to his old self.
